title: Hossanna Halleluiya
lyrics:
Hossanna Halleluiya  -4
“Bwi jerusalemni gwthar mwndira
Manwba rongza khandwng “-2
(A)
Papi buhum khou fwjakhangnw
Gwmanai subung khou naigirfinnw -2
Daogabwgou gada bisayao  daogabwgou -2
(B)
Khwmse hadorkhou swrang hwnw
Haoria gwsw khou gwjwn hwnw -2
Daogabwgou gada bisayao  daogabwgou -2
